   },
   {
    "narration": "没错，我在一年前见过……@鹤乃这空虚的表情……",
    "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101716/vo_full_101716-2-6"
   },
   {
    "narration": "那时候是刚从游乐园玩耍归来@我以为她只是因为闹得太欢@所以累到没有精神",
    "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101716/vo_full_101716-2-7",
    "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101716/vo_full_101716-2-6"
   },
   {
    "narration": "但是……",
