    "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101716/vo_full_101716-2-12",
    "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101716/vo_full_101716-2-11"
   },
   {
    "narration": "那时的鹤乃@只是从一直积攒的压力中得到解放@因而感到安心而已……",
    "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101716/vo_full_101716-2-13",
