    "narrationEffect": "in",
    "turnChangeOut": "fadeOut"
   },
   {
    "narration": "那天之所以会去游乐园@本是为了让因失去梅露而不安的队员们@重新振作起来……",
    "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101716/vo_full_101716-2-14"
   },
   {
    "narration": "那个时候的鹤乃@已经隐隐察觉到了梅露消失的缘由",
    "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101716/vo_full_101716-2-15",
    "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101716/vo_full_101716-2-14"
   },
   {
    "narration": "或许她一边责怪着自己@一边忍耐着痛苦……",
    "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101716/vo_full_101716-2-16",
